These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, spanish, american, german, nigerian, egyptian, russian
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: handball, snowboarding, soccer, water-polo, surfing, basketball, cricket
 1. the argentine is between the german and the russian##2
 2. the spanish is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the nigerian is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the german##1
 7. the person who's sport is handball is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 8. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the russian##1
 9. the nigerian is on the left of the egyptian##1
10. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
11. the egyptian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Nationality   | german | argentine | russian | spanish    | american | nigerian   | egyptian    |
| Sport         | basketball  | snowboarding   | water-polo | handball | soccer   | cricket | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: lemon, papaya, apricot, broccoli, plum, pear, raspberry
There are 7 different nationalities: thai, indian, colombian, argentine, brazilian, indonesian, dutch
1. the indonesian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating apricot is between the person eating pear and the indonesian##2
3. the indian is on the right of the thai##1
4. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the colombian##1
5. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
6. the brazilian is on the left of the thai##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
8. the person eating plum is on the left of the argentine##1
9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Food          | plum | apricot | pear | papaya | raspberry | lemon      | broccoli  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | argentine  | dutch     | colombian     | brazilian  | thai | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-3::.
There are 7 different nationalities: british, turkish, chinese, brazilian, japanese, spanish, argentine
7 different pets are kept: hedgehog, bird, lizard, cat, frog, mouse, guinea-pig
 1. the japanese is on the left of the british##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 3. the owner of the frog is the argentine##1
 4. the chinese is on the left of the spanish##1
 5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 6. the brazilian is the owner of the cat##1
 7. the british is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the brazilian##2
 9. the british is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the turkish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7     |
| Nationality   | argentine | japanese | british | turkish   | brazilian | chinese | spanish |
| Pet           | frog | mouse     | bird     | lizard | cat   | hedgehog   | guinea-pig    |

