.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk, cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, thai, spanish, italian, indian, german, egyptian
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the spanish##1
 2. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indian##1
 3. the german is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the indian##1
 5. the russian is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the italian is between the person drinking coffee and the german##2
 7. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
 8. the italian is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is the thai##1
10. the russian is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Beverage      | coffee    | cola  | almond-milk  | 7up  | mirinda      | hot-chocolate       | soy-milk |
| Nationality   | indian | italian | german | egyptian | russian | spanish | thai  |

