.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: trance, gospel, r&b, d&b, blues, salsa, reggae
The people use 7 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, scooter, quad-bike, bus, car, boat
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is between the fan of reggae and the fan of trance##2
4. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the car is on the left of the fan of trance##1
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
8. the person driving the airplane is the fan of d&b##1
9. the fan of blues is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | d&b      | blues | trance | r&b | reggae      | gospel      | salsa |
| Transport     | airplane | car | boat       | jet-ski | scooter | bus | quad-bike |

