.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-6::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, journalist, teacher, social-worker, accountant, coach
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, skateboarding, basketball, rugby, skiing, volleyball, golf
1. the journalist is on the left of the coach##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is the social-worker##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the chef is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
5. the accountant is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is skiing and the software-developer##2
7. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
8. the accountant is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Job     | social-worker | software-developer | teacher | accountant | chef | journalist     | coach |
| Sport   | basketball   | rugby    | golf    | skiing      | skateboarding  | biathlon | volleyball |

