.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, juice, sprite, almond-milk, soy-milk, water
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: weightlifting, badminton, skateboarding, soccer, basketball, handball, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is handball is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking juice is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is basketball and the person drinking almond-milk##2
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Beverage   | 7up | tea    | sprite | juice   | soy-milk | water    | almond-milk |
| Sport      | soccer | weightlifting | snowboarding    | badminton | basketball    | skateboarding | handball  |

