.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-8::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, sprite, soy-milk, 7up, iced-tea, milk
The people have 7 different jobs:  security-guard, dancer, project-manager, designer, electrician, manager, chef
 1. the electrician is on the left of the designer##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left of the project-manager##1
 3. the manager is on the far left##1
 4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 5. the electrician is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking milk##2
 7. the dancer is on the right of the manager##1
 8. the security-guard is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking almond-milk##2
11. the electrician is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | sprite  | 7up   | almond-milk         | coffee     | milk              | iced-tea    | soy-milk     |
| Job        | manager | dancer | electrician | designer | chef | security-guard | project-manager |

