.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, crime, spy, western, time-travel, fantasy
The people use 7 different means of transport: van, scooter, roller, airplane, snowmobile, car, train
1. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching western movies is between the person driving the train and the person driving the snowmobile##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
5. the person driving the van is in the middle##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
7. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
9. the person driving the train is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |   3    |    4    |    5     |     6     |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | spy     | time-travel | western | crime | fantasy  | animation |
| Transport     | roller | airplane | snowmobile   | van     | train    | scooter | car   |

