.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-10::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, water, almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 7 different hobbies: woodworking, dancing, card-games, puzzles, reading, fishing, video-games
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is puzzles and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is fishing##2
9. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4       |    5    |      6      |    7    |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | juice       | iced-tea         | water         | soy-milk   | hot-chocolate        | almond-milk |
| Hobby      | video-games | card-games | woodworking | reading | dancing | fishing | puzzles  |

