5. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's hobby is camping##2
7. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is baking##2
8. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
9. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
