.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-12::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, drama, crime, thriller, time-travel, sports
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, d&b, country, jazz, metal, rock, hip-hop
 1. the person watching family movies is the fan of hip-hop##1
 2. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person watching family movies is between the person watching crime movies and the fan of soul##2
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
 5. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the fan of country is on the right of the fan of soul##1
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
 8. the person watching drama movies is the fan of metal##1
 9. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
10. the fan of jazz is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3   |   4   |    5    |   6    |   7    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | family | fantasy  | thriller   | time-travel | sports | drama |
| Music-Genre   | jazz     | hip-hop       | soul | country | rock  | d&b   | metal   |

