 5. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 6. the person eating potato is the person drinking sprite##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person drinking coffee and the person eating potato##2
