 6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person eating kale is the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the person eating banana is the person eating banana##1
 9. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
10. the person eating banana is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2    |     3     |       4       |      5      |    6     |    7     |
| Beverage   | sprite       | tea | coffee      | 7up | juice       | almond-milk | soy-milk |
